    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Holding a small sprig that once carried edible berries, you ask for nature's blessing and magically regrow the berries, now instilled with healing magic.</em></span></p><p><strong>Healing</strong></p><ul><li><p>Eight berries* appear in your hand. A creature can use their action to eat up to eight berries, or a creature can use their action to feed a berry to another creature, including unconscious creatures. Eating a berry restores 1 hit point.</p></li></ul></div><p></p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">*</strong></span><strong>Upcasting</strong>: Create four more berries for each spell level above 1st.</p></div></div></div></div><p><em>A creature that cannot swallow or digest the berry cannot gain hit points from this spell.</em></p>",
            "chat": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><strong>Healing</strong></p><ul><li><p>Eight berries* appear in your hand. A creature can use their action to eat up to eight berries, or a creature can use their action to feed a berry to another creature, including unconscious creatures. Eating a berry restores 1 hit point.</p></li></ul></div><p></p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">*</strong></span><strong>Upcasting</strong>: Create four more berries for each spell level above 1st.</p></div></div></div></div><p><em>A creature that cannot swallow or digest the berry cannot gain hit points from this spell.</em></p>"
